title: Episode 57 ft Nat D from Mob Wives
itunes:title: Episode 57 ft Nat D from Mob Wives
description:
Nat D from Mob Wives chops it up with Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago and Gigi Maguire about dating men who wear suits, happy endings for women, lame guys with money and guys who leave bad tips or no tips. Natalie discusses forgiving her ex husband for cheating and taking him back, being “addicted” to an ex, and a “manly man” who pretended to suck a d* in bed.
